                            <h3>How far in advance should I book my flights?</h3>
                            <p>It is advisable to book your flights at least 45 days before your departure date. This timeframe increases your chances of securing affordable fares and better seat selections.</p>
                            <h3>How can I choose the right destination for my trip?</h3>
