                            <h3>What should I book in advance besides flights?</h3>
                            <p>In addition to flights, it’s crucial to book hotels, bus, and train tickets in advance. Pre-booking ensures you can find the best deals and availability, particularly during peak travel seasons.</p>
                            <h3>How can I effectively plan my daily itinerary?</h3>
